description:
F.E.A.R. Files uses combat adaptable AI to provide an intense &quot;action movie&quot; experience while keeping players engrossed in it's spine-chilling storylines. Gamers will assume the roles of an elite soldier trained in combating unusual and unimaginable situations. Called in to confront a mysterious force, the player must escape from a crisis spiraling out of control. F.E.A.R. Files contains two F.E.A.R. missions (the all-new F.E.A.R. Perseus Mandate campaign, as well as F.E.A.R. Extraction Point) which provide the player with a unique fusion of stylized first-person shooter and supernatural suspense that will keep gamers at the edge of their seats. 


Release Date: November 6, 2007
M for Mature: Blood and Gore, Intense Violence, Strong Language 
Genre: First-Person  Shooter 
Publisher: Sierra 
Developers: TimeGate , Day 1 Studios
Language: English
Region: Region Free
